      "beast_baseline": "wait sorry, what did you mean by the goblin thing? i'm just trying to learn the actual biochemistry for the exam. can you stick to the molecular part? like, tell me about the binding sites and the difference between how it hits cox-1 vs cox-2 specifically.",
